title: Print, 1756
creditline: Gift of Eleanor and Sarah Hewitt
description: Escutcheon with the title of a map of Westphalia.  The left top corner of the map.  Rocaille frame intertwined with a garland.  A trophy of arms with the shooting cannons is on top.
